(1)
for (i in 0 .. 5){
    println(i)
}

->0 1 2 3 4 5

(2)
for (i in 5 downTo 0){
    println(i)
}

-> 5 4 3 2 1 0

(3)
for (i in 0 until 5) {
    println(i)
}
//////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
val list = arrayListOf<Int>(1, 2, 3, 4, 5)

for (i in 0 until list.size){
    println(list[i])
}
-> 0 1 2 3 4
輸出結果相同
但程式比較易讀
